### CheckPoint — Admin News endpoints
### Requires an ADMIN account. See admin-users.http for the login request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_HERE

### Create a news article (draft)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/news
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New roadmap published",
  "description": "We just shipped the public roadmap. Check it out!",
  "picture": "https://example.com/cover.jpg"
}

### List all news articles (drafts + published, paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/news?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get a single news article by id (any status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/news/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a news article
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/news/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "description": "Updated content.",
  "picture": "https://example.com/new-cover.jpg"
}

### Publish a news article
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/news/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Unpublish a news article (back to draft)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/news/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/unpublish
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete a news article
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/news/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Trigger a news import from an external source (MANUAL | STEAM | RSS)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/news/import/RSS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
